{"serial": "11071", "department_serial": 12, "code": "CL4065", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Oracle Bone Inscriptions", "ch": "甲骨文"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Hu,Yun-Feng"], "ch": ["胡雲鳳"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "111"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "中國文學系", "en": "Department of Chinese Literature"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 3, "selected": 50, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "一是甲骨學的基礎知識；\n二是釋讀由殷商至周初的甲骨文資料；\n三是結合甲骨文及傳世文獻的研讀，討論上古文化與社會制度。", "en": "One is the basic knowledge of oracle bone science;\nThe second is to interpret oracle bone inscriptions from the Yin Shang Dynasty to the early Zhou Dynasty;\nThe third is to discuss ancient culture and social systems based on the study of oracle bone inscriptions and handed down documents."}, "outline": {"ch": "1  甲骨四堂簡介\n2  甲骨學簡史\n3 干支表及先公先王表\n5 甲骨文字構形特點\n6 甲骨文的六書與三書\n7 甲骨文分期與分類\n8 甲骨文導讀(一)：戰爭、田獵\n9 期中考\n10 甲骨文導讀(二)：祭祀\n11 甲骨文導讀(三)：氣象、農業\n12 甲骨文導讀(四)：生育、疾病\n13 甲骨文導讀(五)：卜旬卜辭、周祭卜辭\n14 甲骨文導讀(六)：記事刻辭、周原甲骨\n15 甲骨文的價值與應用\n16 期末考試", "en": "1 Introduction to the Four Oracle Bone Halls\n2 A brief history of oracle bone science\n3 Table of stems and branches and table of ancestors and kings\n5. Characteristics of the configuration of oracle bone characters\n6 The Six and Three Books of Oracle Bone Inscriptions\n7 Oracle staging and classification\n8 Introduction to Oracle Bone Inscriptions (1): War, Hunting\n9 midterm exam\n10 Introduction to Oracle Bone Inscriptions (2): Sacrifice\n11 Introduction to Oracle Bone Inscriptions (3): Meteorology, Agriculture\n12 Introduction to Oracle Bone Inscriptions (4): Fertility and Disease\n13 Introduction to Oracle Bone Inscriptions (V): Divination of the Xun Dynasty and Divination of the Zhou Sacrifice\n14 Introduction to Oracle Bone Inscriptions (6): Recording Inscriptions, Zhouyuan Oracle Bones\n15 The value and application of Oracle\n16 Final Exam"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. 張秉權《甲骨文與甲骨學》國立編譯館，1988。\n2. 中國科學院考古研究所編《甲骨文編》中華書局，1978。\n3. 朱歧祥《甲骨文讀本》里仁書局，2010。", "en": "1. Zhang Bingquan, “Oracle Bone Inscriptions and Oracle Bone Science“, National Compilation and Translation Center, 1988.\n2. “Oracle Bone Inscriptions“ compiled by the Institute of Archeology, Chinese Academy of Sciences, Zhonghua Book Company, 1978.\n3. Zhu Qixiang‘s “Oracle Bone Inscriptions Reader“ Liren Bookstore, 2010."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100%", "en": "100%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "", "", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1. 平時成績：40％\n2. 期中成績：30％\n3. 期末成績：30％“", "en": "1. Usual score: 40％\n2. Midterm grade: 30％\n3. Final grade: 30％“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "請事先與教師約時間。", "en": "Please make an appointment with the teacher in advance."}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "語言文字", "en": "語言文字"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "文獻解讀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "無"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯思辨", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "無"]}, {"competencies": "語文表達", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "無"]}, {"competencies": "文學鑑賞", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "無"]}, {"competencies": "人文素養與國際視野", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "無"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Interpreting classics", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance", "No assessment"]}, {"competencies": "Logical thinking", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance", "No assessme